See these sections for further information:

FeedItem:: For information on the structure, collection and database storage and retrieval of items from RSS/Atom feeds.
BayesClassifier:: For information on the way the Bayes classifier is integrated into Winnow.
Bayes:: For information on the Bayes classifier itself.
FeedItemTokenizer:: For information on how a FeedItem is broken up into tokens for use by the classifier.
Tagging:: For information on the tagging model used by Winnow.